lass="caption text-center">\r\n<h4>District Governor\r\n(2010-11)</h4>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 c1">\r\n<figure class="thumbnail">\r\n<div class="thumb-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive wp-post-image" src="http://nagarajafor2ndvp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/9.png" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" alt="Adrian Eli" width="490" height="560" />\r\n<div class="team-social"></div>\r\n<!-- .team-social -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- .thumb-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<figcaption class="caption text-center">\r\n<h4>Excellence in Education and Training Award\r\n2010</h4>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-2 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 empt"></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 c3">\r\n<figure class="thumbnail">\r\n<div class="thumb-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive wp-post-image" src="http://nagarajafor2ndvp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/4.png" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" alt="Adrian Eli" width="490" height="560" />\r\n<div class="team-social"></div>\r\n<!-- .team-social -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- .thumb-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<figcaption class="caption text-center">\r\n<h4>Lt. Governor Education and Training\r\n(2009-10)</h4>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 hidden-lg hidden-xs hidden-md ipad"></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 c3">\r\n<figure class="thumbnail">\r\n<div class="thumb-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive wp-post-image" src="http://nagarajafor2ndvp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/10.png" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" alt="Adrian Eli" width="490" height="560" />\r\n<div class="team-social"></div>\r\n<!-- .team-social -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- .thumb-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<figcaption class="caption text-center">\r\n<h4>Distinguished Toastmaster\r\n2008</h4>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 c3">\r\n<figure class="thumbnail">\r\n<div class="thumb-wrapper">\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive wp-post-image" src="http://nagarajafor2ndvp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/3.png" sizes="(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px" alt="Adrian Eli" width="490" height="560" />\r\n<div class="team-social"></div>\r\n<!-- .team-social -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- .thumb-wrapper -->\r\n\r\n<figcaption class="caption text-center">\r\n<h4>District PRO and\r\nConference Chair\r\n(2007-08)</h4>\r\n</figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_wp_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="4007" overlay_color="yes" full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1508963073921{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}" el_id="testimonials"][vc_column][tt_section_title title_alignment="text-center" title_color_option="custom-color" section_separator="no" title="- testimonials" title_color="#ffffff"][/tt_section_title][tt_testimonials][tt_testimonial photo_option="no" client_name="MANOJ VASUDEVAN â€“" client_org=" Author of International bestseller â€œMastering Leadership The Mousetrap Way``"]"I first met Nagaraja Rao in 2015 at Las Vegas. Since then, I have come to admire his versatility in building a booming coffee business, serving Toastmasters and still dedicating quality time for his family. During my many trips to India, I have noticed that he has earned the appreciation and respect of a large number of people across the country. He makes a big difference by how he builds teams and selflessly allows others to grow into leaders. As an international leadership coach and as someone who studies leaders from around the world, I view Nagaraja as a case study of how, with proper planning, strategy and execution, someone from a humble background can rise into exceptional leadership positions at a global level. When I enquired â€œWhat makes large multinational companies choose you as their manufacturing partner?â€ Nagarajaâ€™s answer summarises, who he is. He said â€œIt is because they trust us.â€ With his decades of experience in leading both â€˜for-profitâ€™ and â€˜not-for-profitâ€™ organisations, Nagaraja has acquired a unique blend of business acumen and service mentality. I believe he can make a tremendous contribution to the organisation."[/tt_testimonial][tt_testimonial photo_option="no" client_name="SUBBI P MATHUR,PHD., DTM - " client_org="Past Region Advisor, Region 8, USA"]"It is my pleasure to endorse the Candidacy of Nagaraja Rao, DTM, PID, PRA for Second Vice President of our wonderful organization. We need seasoned multifaceted leaders like him to lead us towards greater success. His experience as a Region Advisor, International Director and a Business Owner has given him the unique distinction of having both a â€˜birdâ€™s eye viewâ€™ and a â€˜grass roots level perspectiveâ€ His penchant for collaborative decision making and developing international partnerships has enabled him to develop a compelling vision for the future of Toastmasters.\r\nI have personally known Nagaraja since 2010. I was impressed with his attitude of respect and true friendship not only towards me but to members from around the world. I have seen him grow in stature and maturity over the years. He and his wife Arathi are charming and truly treat Toastmasters as their family members. We shall have a caring, energetic and hardworking leader in Nagaraja Rao. I support his candidacy with all my heart."[/tt_testimonial][tt_testimonial photo_option="no" client_name="KELLY GUO, DTM â€“ " client_org="Past District Director, D89, China"]"To me, Nagaraja Rao has been highly successful in all aspects of his life. He is a person full of life wisdom, adroitly balancing work, family, and Toastmasters. It was my honor to work with him as a Program Quality Director and a District Director while he was serving as an International Director. By being supportive and responsive to our requests and concerns, he made a big difference! I admire his leadership style - calm and patient when faced with challenges and always making people feel comfortable. He is my role model.\r\nOne of the things I truly appreciate about Nagaraja is that he knows how to encourage and show his care and he also knows the right moment to do it. I still remember his valuable â€œleadership wisdomâ€ which I received through email when I just got elected as District director. It had only 10 sentences but they were the quintessence of leadership. It inspired me, showed me the right direction and equipped me with confidence to lead as a District Director.\r\nIt will be invaluable for Toastmasters International to have him continue to serve in the top leadership. He has my wholehearted endorsement for the position of Second Vice President."[/tt_testimonial][tt_testimonial photo_option="no" client_name="KIMINARI AZUMA, DTM â€“ " client_org="Past District Director, D76, Japan"]"I had the pleasure of working with Nagaraja Rao for three years when I was the LGM, LGET and DD of District 76, Japan. He has visited us many times for delivering keynotes, training district leaders, and presenting corporate recognitions. I am particularly impressed by his integrity and his desire to help people. He is a gifted storyteller who inspires people to give their best by sharing his experience and values.\r\n\r\nAlthough he and I were born in different parts of the world and grew up in different cultures, I feel a strong sense of connection with him. To me, he personifies the ideal of servant leadership.â€\r\n[/tt_testimonial][tt_testimonial photo_option="no" client_name="Dananjaya Hettiarachchi â€“ " client_org="World Champion of Public Speaking, 2014"]<span style="font-weight: 400;">"Nagaraja Rao is an exemplary servant leader who has a proven track record in grooming talent. A founding pillar in the south Asian Toastmasters movement he has proven himself over and over again as a leader, a mentor and a prominent industry captain in India. Personally Nagaraja has been a mentor in my own journey, imparting invaluable advice and skills that have made a real difference to my development over the years. A humble human being who combines his passion for excellence with leadership, Nagaraja has set a standard for all of us to follow when it comes to selfless leadership. A visionary, exemplary human being and moreover a man worth following."</span>[/tt_testimonial][/tt_testimonials][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1513244656905{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 120px !important;background-color: #ddd !important;}"][vc_column el_id="blogs"][tt_section_title title_alignment="text-center" title_color_option="custom-color" section_separator="no" title="- Blogs" title_color="#ffffff"][/tt_section_title][tt_latest_post post_limit="3" grid_column="4" word_limit="15" show_all_button="yes" button_text="All Blogs" custom_link="url:http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%2Frazorbee%2Fnagaraja%2Findex.php%2Fblog%2F|||"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row overlay_color="yes" css=".vc_custom_1508602436465{margin-bottom: 0px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_class="overflow-hidden"][vc_column css=".vc_custom_1453227646256{padding-top: 140px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;}" offset="vc_col-md-6"][vc_custom_heading text="Message from Nagaraja Rao " font_container="tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" google_fonts="font_family:Roboto%20Slab%3A100%2C300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1508956508183{margin-bottom: 25px !important;}"][vc_column_text el_class="white-text"]Conveniently disseminate quality niche markets after just in time results. Seamlessly exploit synergistic technologies whereas customer directed "outside the box" thinking. Conveniently revolutionize resource sucking schemas vis-a-vis equity invested sources. technologies whereas cu